---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = "June 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Democratic AI Consulting — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="pt-44 pb-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-coral mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-[36px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-mute mb-12">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="prose-content space-y-8 text-[16px] text-mute leading-body">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Who we are</h2>
          <p>Democratic AI Consulting is a boutique AI consulting practice operated by Austin Quinn, located in New York, NY. Our website is <a href="https://demoaiconsulting.com" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">demoaiconsulting.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Information we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We collect information in the following ways:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Booking information.</strong> When you book a call through Cal.com, Cal.com collects your name, email address, and any notes you provide. This information is subject to Cal.com's privacy policy.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Analytics.</strong> We use Plausible Analytics, a privacy-focused analytics tool that does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information. Plausible collects aggregate data about page visits.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Contact information.</strong> If you contact us directly, we receive any information you include in that message.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">How we use your information</h2>
          <p>We use the information we collect to respond to inquiries, schedule and conduct consultations, and improve this website. We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties except as described in this policy or as required by law.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Cookies</h2>
          <p>This website does not use cookies for tracking or advertising. Plausible Analytics, our analytics provider, operates without cookies. Cal.com may set cookies when you visit their booking interface. See our <a href="/cookies" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">Cookie Notice</a> for more details.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We use the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Cal.com</strong> for appointment scheduling. <a href="https://cal.com/privacy" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cal.com Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Plausible Analytics</strong> for website analytics. <a href="https://plausible.io/privacy" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plausible Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink font-medium">Vercel</strong> for website hosting. <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Your rights</h2>
          <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal information we hold about you by contacting us at <a href="mailto:austinquinn1999@gmail.com" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">austinquinn1999@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page reflects the most recent update. Continued use of the website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>Democratic AI Consulting<br />Austin Quinn<br />New York, NY<br /><a href="mailto:austinquinn1999@gmail.com" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">austinquinn1999@gmail.com</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
